The paper discusses the use of Datalog and logic-based languages for graph and data mining algorithms, which falls under the category of databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the use of aggregates in recursion, which is a topic in logic (cs.LO). The paper further discusses parallel execution and distributed systems, which falls under the categories of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC, cs.DS). Finally, the paper discusses the evaluation of recursive queries, which is a topic in programming languages (cs.PL).
